Mon Mar  1 22:00
  Gabriel Plutzar
+ included support for generic new keyword for LogLevels                       
  * LogLevels <string>                                               
    You can specify all Loglevels you want in your log               
    Default is 123456789, use 23456789 if you don't want all the IDLE
    sessions in your logfile (eg when you start hpt once a minute)   
  + Major Changes in log.c & log.h were necessary to supress unwanted
    log file entries in IDLE only hpt sessions (like regularily scanning
    the netmail area without something happening worth logging)
  + Changes to the code to force all unneeded log entries to loglevel 1

