Sat Feb 20 20:48:03 MET 1999
  Tobias Ernst:
+ Added support for QQQ files. If found in the tempOutbound, they will be
  packed into the outgoing arcmail bundle. This is useful if you use
  CFRoute: You can point CFRoutes tempOutbound to the fidoconfig tempOut,
  in order to pack netmail into arcmail bundles.	
+ Added support for packet forwarding. See the fidoconfig manual for
  information.	 
	
